SVM Tutorial.
Usage: ptyhon3 doc_class.py [C [kernel [degree [OPTION(S)]]]]

C and kernel are the only mandatory arguments.
Degree defaults at 3 if omitted.

Available options:
-q, --real-queries     Tests on real queries after calculating
                         the confusion matrix.
-s, --show-urls        Shows training URLs. Very long output.
-h, --help             This help text.
